Sentencas: La0.8Sr0.2Mn1-xScxO3-delta perovskite oxides (x = 0.00, 0.05, 0.10, 0.15) were systematically examined as cathode materials for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Investigation of structural, electrical and electrochemical properties of La0.8Sr0.2Mn1-xScxO3-δ as cathode on yttria-stabilized zirconia electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell fabricated by one step dry pressing method

Sentencas: This study encompassed structural attributes, temperature-dependent weight variations, the electrical conductivity of La0.8Sr0.2Mn1-xScxO3-delta compositions, and the single-cell electrochemical performance of La0.8Sr0.2Mn1-xScxO3-delta on yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ).
Titulo: Investigation of structural, electrical and electrochemical properties of La0.8Sr0.2Mn1-xScxO3-δ as cathode on yttria-stabilized zirconia electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell fabricated by one step dry pressing method

Sentencas: Further characterizations were carried out through powder X-ray diffraction (XRD), thermogravimetric analysis, DC four-probe method, and impedance spectroscopy, respectively.
Titulo: Investigation of structural, electrical and electrochemical properties of La0.8Sr0.2Mn1-xScxO3-δ as cathode on yttria-stabilized zirconia electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell fabricated by one step dry pressing method

Sentencas: The X-ray diffraction (XRD) analysis revealed a clear correlation between the increase in Sc3+ content at the B-site and an increase in both the lattice parameter and lattice volume.
Titulo: Investigation of structural, electrical and electrochemical properties of La0.8Sr0.2Mn1-xScxO3-δ as cathode on yttria-stabilized zirconia electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell fabricated by one step dry pressing method

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity of La0.8Sr0.2Mn1-xScxO3-delta compounds at 750 C-degrees were found to be 137.941, 198.07, 119.789, and 61.036 S cm(-1) for x = 0.00, x = 0.05, x = 0.10, and x = 0.15, respectively.
Titulo: Investigation of structural, electrical and electrochemical properties of La0.8Sr0.2Mn1-xScxO3-δ as cathode on yttria-stabilized zirconia electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell fabricated by one step dry pressing method

Sentencas: When combined with YSZ in a single cell, the area-specific resistances for La0.8Sr0.2Mn1-xScxO3-delta were varied between 0.56 and 2.2 Omega cm(2).
Titulo: Investigation of structural, electrical and electrochemical properties of La0.8Sr0.2Mn1-xScxO3-δ as cathode on yttria-stabilized zirconia electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell fabricated by one step dry pressing method

Sentencas: La0.8Sr0.2Mn1-xScxO3-delta exhibited enhanced electrocatalytic activity, with an exchange current density of 39.35 mA cm(-2 )at 750 C-degrees suggesting the composition as a potential candidate for cathode material in IT-SOFC.
Titulo: Investigation of structural, electrical and electrochemical properties of La0.8Sr0.2Mn1-xScxO3-δ as cathode on yttria-stabilized zirconia electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell fabricated by one step dry pressing method
